{"tid":2463212,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 返工撞到劉祖達","createTime":"2021-03-26T13:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:38:25.000Z","uid":3204,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08502a46bcea2acc57e74840ee67f742fd6893c6","tid":2463212,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，件事大概係2個月前左右，由於我政治凍感嘅關係，事前喺真喺我唔識香港嘅政治巨星。<br />\n<br />\n小妹是做酒店reception嘅，有一日，finn出現喺大堂個lobby，而我就喺唯一一個企緊counter，佢就行埋嚟問我嘢，我重申一次，我嗰刻真的不知道佢是誰。<br />\n<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\njudy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有咩可以幫到你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有冇得睇下你哋個ball房<br />\n心諗乜撚嘢ball房呀屌你老母，冇受過教育？<br />\nBallroom就Ballroom啦，我記得嗰時係夜晚9點幾同個ballroom有event做緊，佢嗰樣仲要好撚臭寸<br />\n再加上睇ballroom喺要搵event sales預約時間先可以睇，唔撚喺話睇就睇，你估你喺大明星？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔好意思先生，我哋而家個ballroom有event進行緊，如果要睇嘅話(比咗張酒店卡片佢)，可以同我哋event sales預約返個時間呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下？你哋而家冇sell屎咩？<br />\n屌你，9點幾收撚哂工啦，嗰腦裝屎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 𠵱嗰時間都多數已經收哂工架啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哈，咁準時呀，咁你叫你經理出來，你幫唔到我。<br />\n嗰一刻已經好想一巴車落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好呀，請問先生貴姓呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我喎！(佢指著自己個樣)<br />\n心諗who the fuck are you? 我再問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :0貴姓？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你叫你經理出嚟啦，你經理會識得我。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 請你等等。<br />\n<br />\n最正喺。。。我經理。。。唔識講廣東話，黑人嚟，識鬼香港政治人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Good evening dwarf, how may I help you?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Er... I want see ballroom.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : I am very sorry that there&rsquo;s an event on going in the ballroom which is quite impossible to show you. But you may contact our event sales associate for any further questions. (又比張酒店卡片佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thank you<br />\n佢望一望經理，望一望張卡片，再望一望我，之後就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後經理問我佢邊位，我話我都唔識佢，之後我都係問同事先知道佢原來喺攬鈔巴。"},{"pid":"9933df411904ee56ad1c9f34ef4ffe4c3e84463c","tid":2463212,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"唔睇呢個post都唔知邊個攬鈔巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26c65305928d1f9d4fdaf70d12e38ed59682999","tid":2463212,"uid":384468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9933df411904ee56ad1c9f34ef4ffe4c3e84463c","tid":2463212,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"唔睇呢個post都唔知邊個攬鈔巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"原來呢條撚樣就係攬妙巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b9ca054fb4bd550b7c